{"lemma":"واعِد","slug":"واعِد","root":"#.ع.د","root_slug":"_-ع-د","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ع-د","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"واعِد","root":"وعد","pos":"V","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n42119"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B9%D9%90%D8%AF"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to agree on a meeting with, to appoint","tags":["ditransitive"],"examples":[{"text":"وَوَاعَدْنَا مُوسَىٰ ثَلَاثِينَ لَيْلَةً وَأَتْمَمْنَاهَا بِعَشْرٍ"},{"text":"وَلَٰكِنْ لَا تُوَاعِدُوهُنَّ سِرًّا إِلَّا أَنْ تَقُولُوا قَوْلًا مَعْرُوفًا"}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"promising"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of وَعَدَ (waʕada, “to promise”)."},"ipa":["/waː.ʕa.da/","/waː.ʕid/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n42119","headword_ar":"وَاعِدٌ","root":"wEd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  A horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that promises run after run."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)  A beast"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that promises to be productive of good, and fortunate."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) (tropical:)  See an ex. in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSodaq","text_ar":"مَصْدَق"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  (tropical:)  A tree, or herbage,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"promising good produce."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  A cloud,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which, as it were, promises rain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) ―         -b5-  (tropical:)  A day"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which promises heat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) as also a year: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which the commencement promises heat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN waAEidapN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ وَاعِدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land of which the herbage is hoped to prove good and productive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, A, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of its first appearance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, L.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","As","S","A","L","K"]}]}}